43:45.694 --> 43:47.593
How did you know
to come here?

43:47.595 --> 43:49.528
           Joey brought me once,

43:49.530 --> 43:51.696
           one day he said
           he wanted to see you.

43:51.698 --> 43:53.097
And where was I?

43:53.099 --> 43:55.666
               I don't know.
