44:16.552 --> 44:18.018
     so I have to get back

44:18.020 --> 44:19.219
               before she has to
               go to work.

44:19.221 --> 44:20.520
     You drove all the way
         into the city

44:20.522 --> 44:21.687
           just to give me this?

44:21.689 --> 44:24.556
          Joe's gone.

44:24.558 --> 44:27.458
That stuff was real important to
             him.

44:27.460 --> 44:29.393
         I didn't know
