44:29.395 --> 44:31.294
 and his mother don't like me,
             so...

44:31.296 --> 44:33.128
So, what do you expect me to do?

44:36.066 --> 44:38.633
    Just, like, be his dad,

44:38.635 --> 44:40.901
you know?

44:43.805 --> 44:46.672
        I've got to go.
  I'm going to get a ticket.

44:53.080 --> 44:56.081
                           Gina?

44:56.083 --> 44:58.583
          Thank you.

44:58.585 --> 45:01.118
             Sure.

46:04.048 --> 46:06.948
       I'll talk to you
